'''帕拉瓦文'''是一种[[婆罗米系文字|婆罗米系文字]]，是在公元4世纪印度南部[[帕拉瓦王朝|帕拉瓦王朝]]周围开发的。

东南亚文字如[[古兰塔文|古兰塔文]]、用[[爪哇字母|爪哇字母]]的[[卡维文|卡维文]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.omniglot.com/writing/javanese.htm |title=Javanese alphabet, pronunciation and language (aksara jawa) |publisher=Omniglot.com |date= |accessdate=2012-03-11 |archive-date=2018-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113144644/http://www.omniglot.com/writing/javanese.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 、[[贝贝因字母|贝贝因字母]]、[[孟语|孟文]]、[[缅文|缅文]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.omniglot.com/writing/burmese.htm |title=Burmese/Myanmar script and pronunciation |publisher=Omniglot.com |date= |accessdate=2012-03-11 |archive-date=2010-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102063348/http://www.omniglot.com/writing/burmese.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 、[[高棉文|高棉文]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.omniglot.com/writing/khmer.htm |title=Khmer/Cambodian alphabet, pronunciation and language |publisher=Omniglot.com |date= |accessdate=2012-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213191456/http://www.omniglot.com/writing/khmer.htm |archive-date=2012-02-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、 [[老傣文|老傣文]]、[[泰文|泰文]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ancientscripts.com/thai.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-10-30 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913224748/http://www.ancientscripts.com/thai.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[老挝文|老挝文]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.omniglot.com/writing/lao.htm |title=Lao alphabet, pronunciation and language |publisher=Omniglot.com |date= |accessdate=2012-03-11 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308165313/https://www.omniglot.com/writing/lao.htm// |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[西双版纳傣文|西双版纳傣文]]是直接或间接派生自帕拉瓦字母表。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://skyknowledge.com/pallava.htm |title=Pallava script |publisher=SkyKnowledge.com |date=2010-12-30 |access-date=2016-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005113001/http://www.skyknowledge.com/pallava.htm |archive-date=2018-10-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==形成==
这里展示的形式是基于公元7世纪的例子。 标有*的字母具有不确定的声音值，因为它们在东南亚几乎很少出現。

===辅音===
每个辅音都有一个固有的/a/，如果没有附加元音符号，它会发声。 如果两个辅音彼此跟随而没有插入元音，则第二辅音被制成下标形式，并且附在第一辅音下面。

